Package be.kuleuven.socialmap.model

Class Summary
FlickrPhoto The FlickrPhoto class represents a geotagged picture posted by a user of flickr.com.
FoursquareVenue The FoursquareVenue class represents a venue registered at foursquare.com.
InstagramPhoto The InstagramPhoto class represents a photo posted by a user of instagr.am.
MapReduceResult The MapReduceResult class represents an element that is the result of a MapReduce operation on a collection of Plottable data.
Plottable Classes that need to be plottable on a map, should extend this class.
Tweet The Tweet class represents a geotagged tweet posted by a user of twitter.com.
